trans-unit.source: Represents a configuration element for a service to be added to the workflow runtime engine.
trans-unit.target: 워크플로 런타임 엔진에 추가되는 서비스의 구성 요소를 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement> specifies a host service that should be initialized and activated by the workflow runtime engine.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement>는 워크플로 런타임 엔진에서 초기화 및 활성화해야 하는 호스트 서비스를 지정합니다.

trans-unit.source: It corresponds to a host service specified in the <`Services`> element in a configuration file.
trans-unit.target: 에 지정 된 호스트 서비스에 해당 하는 것은 <`Services`> 구성 파일의 요소입니다.

trans-unit.source: Because the service specified in a WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement will be initialized by the workflow runtime engine it must have at least one constructor that matches one of the following four signatures (the workflow runtime engine will try to match these signatures in the order shown):
trans-unit.target: WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement에 지정된 서비스는 워크플로 런타임 엔진에 의해 초기화되므로 다음 네 개의 서명 중 하나와 일치하는 생성자가 하나 이상 있어야 합니다. 워크플로 런타임 엔진은 표시된 순서대로 이러한 서명을 일치시킵니다.

trans-unit.source: Service(WorkflowRuntime runtime, NameValueCollection parameters)
Service(WorkflowRuntime runtime)
Service(NameValueCollection parameters)
Service()
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement" /> class.
If you use this constructor, you must explicitly set <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement.Type%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 이 생성자를 사용하는 경우 명시적으로 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement.Type%2A>을 설정해야 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The name of the unrecognized attribute.
The value of the unrecognized attribute.
Called when an unknown attribute is encountered while deserializing the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement" />를 deserialize하는 동안 알 수 없는 특성을 발견할 때 호출됩니다.

trans-unit.source: <see cref="M:System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement.OnDeserializeUnrecognizedAttribute(System.String,System.String)" /> always returns <see langword="true" />.
The name-value pair specified by name and value is added to the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement.Parameters%2A> collection.
trans-unit.target: 이름 및 값으로 지정된 이름-값 쌍이 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement.Parameters%2A> 컬렉션에 추가됩니다.

trans-unit.source: Any attributes other than `type` that are specified in an <`add`> element to the <`Services`> element in the configuration file are added as a name-value pair to the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement.Parameters%2A> collection.
trans-unit.target: 이외의 모든 특성 `type` 에 지정 된 <`add`> 요소를는 <`Services`> 구성 파일의 요소에 이름-값 쌍으로 추가 됩니다는 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement.Parameters%2A> 컬렉션입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the parameters for this service.
A <see cref="T:System.Collections.Specialized.NameValueCollection" /> that specifies the parameters for the service.
Gets or sets the assembly-qualified type name of the service.
trans-unit.target: 서비스의 어셈블리로 한정된 형식 이름을 가져오거나 설정합니다.

trans-unit.source: The assembly-qualified type name of the service.
